{"tid":1516330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[暴大]四院會師做過乜","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:15:39.000Z","uid":199237,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96ec3b071d08ebca1ab66f1e4765b6f36d18035a","tid":1516330,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"四院會師梗係有四七環節<br />\n即係四句七個字嘅野<br />\n<br />\n崇基學院就整呢個<br />\n<br />\n元來警黑一家親<br />\n朗狽為奸面目猙<br />\n鄉黑葉虎白衫軍<br />\n黑官何妖禮樂崩<br />\n<br />\n光榮義士萬人敬<br />\n復歸凡人均無名 <br />\n香城革命由佢領<br />\n港共警黑來認命<br />\n<br />\n時勢險惡念初衷<br />\n代代相承切心痛<br />\n革命起義歸血濃<br />\n命令撤回反送中<br />\n<br />\n來源<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/376586225778832/posts/2193745374062899?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F376586225778832%2Fposts%2F2193745374062899%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkMkuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=ca5ccf08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/376586225778832/posts/2193745374062899?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"eaa9b002bbdd0efe83e9e1c19d55f1f8a861ec15","tid":1516330,"uid":199237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"留意藏頭"},{"pid":"cdf224134475ec1006a3201ea06ad18c5a5876d0","tid":1516330,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n孫子兵法：求其上，得其中；求其中，得其下；求其下，必敗。<br />\n上：中共<br />\n中：林鄭<br />\n下：警犬"},{"pid":"9f6c924037753f5143047a4db86f0c370717f4e6","tid":1516330,"uid":42982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367e63c4b80d8fabb0d5b3e948c33b375a2097b6","tid":1516330,"uid":231818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"3fa9d2eef858d7b53485a4c9be404138ead8a1fa","tid":1516330,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"647b833cb6a0e5e5985370dcf4afbb5e83258df8","tid":1516330,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f6c924037753f5143047a4db86f0c370717f4e6","tid":1516330,"uid":42982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"de94654223d89054f457cffffa48c28ff4b5f365","tid":1516330,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:05:28.000Z","msg":"暴大好野"},{"pid":"0a808597f57a0d6874914baa75bbdf28c0bd60ce","tid":1516330,"uid":162330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"好句好句"},{"pid":"368863a24d10b71f9c50a33b47c2904a9eb2128d","tid":1516330,"uid":303462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f6c924037753f5143047a4db86f0c370717f4e6","tid":1516330,"uid":42982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"而家都5比 會收番嫁"}]}